        </solution>
      </example>

      
    </subsubsection>
    <subsubsection xml:id="subsubsec-Converting-hours-into-seconds">
      <title>Converting hours into seconds</title>
      <p>
        By the conversion above for minutes to hours,seconds to minutes,etc,
      </p>
      <p>
        Convertion of  hours to second, use <m>1 \, hour =3600 \,seconds</m>.
      </p>
      <example>
        <statement>
          <p>
            Convert <m>7 \, hours </m> to seconds.
          </p>
        </statement>
        <solution>
          <p>
            if <m>1 \, hour = 3\,600 \, seconds</m>, Therefore,
          </p>
          <p>
            <md>
              <mrow>7 \, hours= \amp (7 \times 3\,600)\,seconds </mrow>
              <mrow> =\amp 25\,200 \, seconds </mrow>
              
            </md>
          </p>
          <p>
            <m>7 \, hours= 25\,200 \, seconds</m>
          </p>
        </solution>
      </example>
      <example>
        <statement>
          <p>
            Morara covered  a certain distance in <m>2 \, hours</m>. How 
            long did the journey take in seconds?
          </p>
        </statement>
        <solution>
          <p>
            If <m>1 \, hour = 3\,600 \, seconds</m>, therefore, 
          </p>
          <p>
            <md>
              <mrow> 2 \, hours = \amp (2 \times 3\,600) \, seconds </mrow>
              <mrow> =\amp 7\,200  \, seconds</mrow>
              
            </md>
          </p>
          <p>
            The journey took <m>7\,200 \, seconds</m>.
          </p>
        </solution>
      </example>
      
    </subsubsection>
    <subsubsection xml:id="subsubsec-Converting-second-into-hours">
